          <span class='member_constituency'><a href="/constituencies/wiltshire-north" title="Wiltshire North">(North Wiltshire) (Con)</a></span>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Will my hon. Friend give way?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0419P1_20040331_WH_70'>  </a>
